snippet.textDisplay:
Phir Se Chorr Ke Jaane Ke Liye Aa" 
Is Such A Hard Hitting Line.
It's Strange - To Love The Thing That Hurts You. But Maybe It's Not The Song That's Hurting Me. Maybe It's The Truth I Keep Trying To Avoid, Finally Finding A Voice. And Maybe Healing Doesn't Come All At Once. Maybe It Comes In Verses And Refrains - In The Ache That Reminds You You're Still Alive. So I Listen Again. And Again. And Again. Because Somehow, Being Broken By This Song Makes Me Feel Whole.
